# The web app reads from the ONE central env file. There is no separate web env.
#
# Compose:   BACKEND_URL + NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE are injected (compose pins
#            BACKEND_URL=http://api:8000 inside the network).
# Host-run:  set BACKEND_URL when running `pnpm dev`, e.g.
#              BACKEND_URL=http://localhost:8000 pnpm dev
#
# Template + all variables:  ../../infra/.env.example
